Penalty for the premature payment of the credit amount and commission fee for the refinancing of the used credit amount(s) from other financial organizations

In accordance with the term remaining before the credit expiry and with the remainder of the credit principal: \10\10 0% of the prematurely repaid amount if the term remaining before the expiry of the credit is up to 6 months; \10\10 0.5% – if the term remaining before the expiry of the credit is from 6 to 12 months; \10\10 1% – if the term remaining before the expiry of the credit is from 12 to 24 months; \10\10 2% – if the term remaining before the expiry of the credit is over 24 months; \10\10 In case of non-existence/subsequent cancellation of the restrictions established by the law penalty for the premature payment of the credit amount and commission fee for the refinancing of the used credit amount(s) from other financial organizations:- 2% of the prematurely repaid amount irrespective of the period remaining before the expiry of the credit. In any case, regardless of what is defined by the agreement, if the effective law, based on the remaining period of the credit and the remainder of the principal, establishes lesser commission fee, the amount of the commission fee shall be defined in accordance with the rule prescribed by the law
